{"tid":1364398,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【727防具】任何人屋企都有嘅簡易防具","createTime":"2019-07-25T10:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T10:54:41.000Z","uid":259980,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"be137e83113fc59843201a38b52f935bfbd8f238","tid":1364398,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"記住帶<span style=\"color: red;\">攻擊性武器</span>出街係犯法架<br />\n所以我地只會帶<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">比警察叔叔check到都無事</span>嘅防具<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DM9BY8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DM9BY8.jpg&h=8d4f6403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯就係<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">皮帶</span><br />\n皮帶嘅作用係束緊唔合身嘅褲<br />\n戴上皮帶<br />\n喺遇到<span style=\"color: red;\">暴徒想攻擊你</span>時<br />\n合身嘅褲可以幫助你迅速逃走<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔會陷入單方面捱打</span>嘅局面<br />\n想保障自己嘅安全<br />\n最好揀有<span style=\"color: red;\">以下特性</span>嘅皮帶<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1.長</span></span><br />\n所謂一寸長一寸強<br />\n長嘅皮帶可以喺腰度兜多幾圈<br />\n防止褲子喺逃跑時鬆脫<br />\n咁點先叫長呢<br />\n個人認為<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">比起藤條長</span>嘅皮帶都應該可以幫你束緊條褲<br />\n保障安全<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.粗</span></span><br />\n粗嘅皮帶唔易損壞<br />\n仲相當具<span style=\"color: red;\">威嚇力</span><br />\n有條咁粗嘅野喺腰間<br />\n真係<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">黑社會望到都要震兩震</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.金屬皮帶扣</span></span><br />\n金屬皮帶扣比起塑膠扣更穩固<br />\n但使用時要小心<br />\n因為皮帶扣有時<span style=\"color: red;\">幾鋒利</span>下<br />\n一唔小心可能會<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">劃傷皮膚</span><br />\n記得<span style=\"color: red;\">千其唔好</span>比家中小朋友[limegreen]胡亂揮舞[/limegreeen]啊<br />\n<br />\n727<br />\n萬事小心"},{"pid":"0d624cf249948842d31ff0610d58ca03b1299d89","tid":1364398,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:55:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5cacfac8fed1c662a1b17f85456e2b2b597a6a60","tid":1364398,"uid":110332,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:02:50.000Z","msg":"運到過黎？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aUB9B3V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaUB9B3V.png&h=bc91dbc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4bd10a0c4a8270e3c27cf33b6e70707144bdeb6","tid":1364398,"uid":270078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cacfac8fed1c662a1b17f85456e2b2b597a6a60","tid":1364398,"uid":110332,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:02:50.000Z","msg":"運到過黎？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aUB9B3V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaUB9B3V.png&h=bc91dbc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:16:55.000Z","msg":"扣關風險好高， 同埋帶出街俾人周到好煩， 帶行山杖/遮穩陣d"},{"pid":"1636608cee5eef8a88380eb8c43ae80cb6feaf3b","tid":1364398,"uid":270078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:20:24.000Z","msg":"諗認下平底鑊會唔會仲好呢， 進可攻退可守， 係重d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0a004c00e34be7d24a8a79ae63ddccdd94ed88","tid":1364398,"uid":40723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cacfac8fed1c662a1b17f85456e2b2b597a6a60","tid":1364398,"uid":110332,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:02:50.000Z","msg":"運到過黎？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aUB9B3V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaUB9B3V.png&h=bc91dbc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:28:44.000Z","msg":"咪制，畀鬼周到一定入硬<br />\n冷静"},{"pid":"eed7594eb5b4593c3ff83230ec7d8529ba9d0352","tid":1364398,"uid":80303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ayo0LYi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fayo0LYi.png&h=e3efb703&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e212890e6b6